OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:
OL,6,FOutbreaks of rain continuing for
OL,7,Fnorthwest Scotland, perhaps moving
OL,8,Fsouth at times into Northern Ireland.
OL,9,FMainly dry and bright elsewhere, with
OL,10,Fsunny spells. Turning hot across
OL,11,Fsouthern and eastern England.
